text: Dr Chua is very direct and no nonsense but incredibly professional and a kind support. I fell at 7 months and she saw me immediately (despite a busy surgery), was very calm and understanding towards me and reassured me the baby was fine. She gave good guidance throughout the preganancy, although you do need to trust her (I found this very easy) you have chosen her so you should follow her medical advice. I had a very easy and  calm experience with her support and guidance, highly recommend.

Dr Selina is wonderful.
Direct, knowledgeable, empathetic, non-judgmental and no nonsense. If you're looking for modern, progressive and objective advice, she's the one for you. You get no-frills, excellent quality care here. I wouldn't entrust my health/lady parts to anyone else.
I have been very pleased with the direct communication and the medical care that has been provided to me at Selina Chua's women's clinic over the past few years. Highly recommend.
